    "summary": {
      "value": "Shadow Strike reduces MP and causes action loss with swords."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p><strong>Requirements: </strong>you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Darkblade</strong> and <strong>Esper</strong>.</p></blockquote><p>When you hit one or more creatures with an attack from your <strong>Shadow Strike</strong> Skill using a weapon that belongs to the <strong>sword</strong> Category, each of those creatures loses an amount of Mind Points equal to <strong>【the number you rolled on your Might die for Shadow Strike】</strong>. Then, if <strong>【the number you rolled on your Might die for Shadow Strike】 was 8 or higher</strong>, you may choose one creature hit by the attack: if that creature is your <strong>focus</strong> or you have a <strong>Bond</strong> towards them, that creature will perform one fewer action during their next turn (to a minimum of zero actions).</p>",
